text:
Any warrant officer or enlisted member who:
(1) strikes or assaults a warrant officer or noncommissioned officer while that officer is in the execution of official duties;
(2) willfully disobeys the lawful order of a warrant officer or noncommissioned officer; or
(3) treats with contempt or is disrespectful in language or deportment toward a warrant officer or noncommissioned officer while that officer is in the execution of official duties;
shall be punished as a court-martial may direct.
